          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1631108719488-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p><p>Serve the <strong>salmon flakes</strong> over the <strong>parsnip</strong> <strong>röstis</strong></p><p>Top with a <strong>poached egg </strong>and pour over any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>butter sauce </strong>from the pot</p><p>Serve the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>asparagus</strong> to the side and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
